titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: TPRG-SEND TWO YEAR CORRECTED AGE OUTCOME ASSESSMENT SCORE (NEUROMOTOR QUESTION H) - Description

div.p: TPRG-SEND TWO YEAR CORRECTED AGE OUTCOME ASSESSMENT SCORE (NEUROMOTOR QUESTION H) is the PERSON SCORE for question H of the Neuromotor section of the TPRG-SEND Two Year Corrected Age Outcome Assessment.
The question asks "Is this child unable to use hands (i.e. to feed)?".
